## Phase 0 — Baseline Freeze + Regression Checklist

### Goal

Have a stable checklist to compare universal engine behavior against current payment and legacy expectations.

### Codex Prompt

Create a regression checklist document for Payment Voucher and baseline voucher operations.  
Include: register, new, edit, delete/cancel, save, save-and-new behavior, keyboard shortcuts, breadcrumb, validations.  
Do not change code. Add a markdown file under `docs/` called `voucher-regression-checklist.md`.

### Exit Criteria

- Checklist file exists.
- No code changes besides docs.

