## Phase 2 — Receipt Voucher (Polarity Inversion)

### Goal

Add receipt using same UI by flipping DR/CR mapping via profile config.

### Codex Prompt

Implement Phase 2: add receipt voucher type to voucher engine.

Requirements:

- Add receipt profile to `voucherProfiles.ts`:
  - `voucherTypeIds: [3, 29]` (support legacy `[13, 14]` via alias mapping if needed)
  - `supportsCashBankMode: true`
  - `polarity: primarySide=DR, linesDefaultSide=CR`
  - Purposes: primary `CONTRA-CASH|CONTRA-BANK`, lines `RECEIPT-AGAINST`
  - Receipt-specific labels
- Introduce polarity mapping layer so the same header/lines components render DR/CR based on profile.
- Avoid duplicating components; no large voucher-type if/else blocks in UI.
- Receipt should support register/new/edit flows like payment.

Run:

- `npm run lint`
- `npm run build`

### Exit Criteria

- Receipt works end-to-end (create/edit).
- DR/CR inversion is config-driven.

