## Optional Starter Prompt: Master `voucherProfiles.ts`

Use this as a focused starter instruction when beginning profile work:

Create a master `voucherProfiles.ts` for the new voucher engine at  
`src/pages/(main)/apps/accounts/vouchers/voucher/voucherProfiles.ts`.

Requirements:

- Define `VoucherKey` union:
  `payment`, `receipt`, `contra`, `journal`, `sales`, `purchase`, `creditNote`, `debitNote`, `rcmInvoice`, `taxInvoiceBasicSales`, `taxInvoiceBasicPurchase`, `taxInvoiceItemsSales`, `taxInvoiceItemsPurchase`
